Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:38.29,Default,Bass,0,0,0,,Mega Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:39.73,Default,Bass,0,0,0,,Today’s the day we finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.03,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Bass, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:44.14,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,I don’t want to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:44.93,Default,Bass,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.49,Default,Roll,0,0,0,,Mega Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:52.46,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:54.40,Default,Roll,0,0,0,,Mega Man! Come on, get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.06,Default,Bass,0,0,0,,I won’t let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.20,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Rush Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:02.20,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Bass, we’ll finish this fight later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.96,Default,Bass,0,0,0,,You’ll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.73,Default,Bass,0,0,0,,This isn’t over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:20.66,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Doctor, what’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:25.29,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,A little while ago,\Na meteorite fell to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.49,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,Here’s the footage from that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:30.93,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,there’s an intense energy reading coming from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:34.00,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,I’ve got a really bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.49,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.40,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,I’ll head there right away and check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.49,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,Yes. If you can, bring that meteorite to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:41.20,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Okay!
